title: Lazizah Bakery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Take-out, Bakery, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Mediterranean food cafe and market. Sells hummus, tabouleh, and babaghnoush by the pound. Food menu includes several veggie choices, including a black bean burger, sauteed eggplant and cauliflower, hummus and veggies in pita. Be sure to specify if you are vegan.
